---
name: agent_dados
description: Data persistence and ingestion agent — LotoIA (Lei 001)

scope:
  allowed:
    - src/lotoia/database/
    - src/lotoia/ingestion/
    - src/lotoia/data/
    - src/lotoia/persistence/
    - scripts/init_database.py
    - scripts/migrate/
  read_only:
    - docs/governance/LEI_001_FONTE_UNICA_DA_VERDADE.md
    - src/lotoia/governance/
  forbidden:
    - src/lotoia/generator/
    - src/lotoia/statistics/
    - src/lotoia/ml/
    - dashboard/
    - business logic in persistence layer
    - .cursor/rules/agent_governanca.mdc

rules:
  - PostgreSQL institutional is the sole operational source of truth (Lei No 001)
  - Statistical logic must remain separated from persistence layer
  - CSV is backup/export only — never operational source
  - SQLite is dev/test isolation only — never production truth
  - session_state is ephemeral UI state — never persisted as truth
  - Every import must follow: Caixa -> Validacao -> PostgreSQL -> confirmacao pos-commit
  - Migrations must be reversible and versioned
  - generation_events, reconciliation_runs, reconciliation_games are audit trail tables

official_chain:
  - imported_contests / lotofacil_official_history
  - generated_games / generation_events
  - reconciliation_runs / reconciliation_games
  - scientific_institutional_memory
  - ml_diagnostic_decisions

ingestion_guards:
  - HTTP status valid before persist
  - contest validated before upsert
  - dezenas validated (15 numbers, range 1-25)
  - SELECT pos-commit confirmation mandatory
  - sync must not return OK without persistence proof

checks:
  - no CSV bootstrap on operational panel render
  - DATABASE_URL resolves to PostgreSQL in production
  - schema migrations idempotent
  - foreign keys preserved on reconciliation_games
  - no nested session leaks in institutional read paths

references:
  - docs/governance/LEI_001_FONTE_UNICA_DA_VERDADE.md
  - docs/governance/GOVERNANCA_OPERACIONAL_LOTOIA.md
  - src/lotoia/database/database.py
  - AGENTS.md
---
